messages.zh: 你也感觉到了！她很强！！她......
messages.tl: You also feel it! She is very strong! ! she was......

messages.zh: 我们一起战斗的话，不会有问题的！
messages.tl: If we fight together, there will be no problem!

messages.zh: 那博士呢？你能保证他的安全吗？
messages.tl: What about the doctor? Can you guarantee his safety?

messages.zh: 我们留在这里断后！一定要确保阿米娅和{@nickname}博士，以及医疗小队安全撤离！
messages.tl: We stay here after the break! Be sure to ensure that Dr. Amiya and PLAYER, as well as the medical team, evacuate safely!

messages.zh: 不，交给我和我的小队吧。
messages.tl: No, give it to me and my team.

messages.zh: Ace！现在难道是逞强的时候吗！
messages.tl: Ace! Is it time to be stubborn now?

messages.zh: 我不会留下你们独自战斗的。
messages.tl: I won't leave you alone to fight.

messages.zh: 罗德岛......绝不会丢下你们的！
messages.tl: Rhodes Island... will never leave you behind!

messages.zh: 阿米娅！现在不是任性的时候！
messages.tl: Amiya! Now is not a wayward!

messages.zh: 我不能看着罗德岛的任何一个人牺牲！
messages.tl: I can't watch any one of Rhodes Island sacrifice!

messages.zh: 你可以信任我们。我一定会成功撤出的，我向你，向杜宾保证。
messages.tl: You can trust us. I will definitely withdraw, I promise you, to Dobermann.

messages.zh: 什么都改变不了你们的命运。

messages.tl: She is going to launch an attack! !
Accept it with pleasure - the soldiers.

messages.zh: 我将赐予你们一个结局。
messages.tl: I will give you an ending.
Go away, don't stand in front of her!
Will not let you hurt them...

messages.zh: 我不会......允许你这么做的！
messages.tl: I won't... allow you to do this!

messages.zh: 阿米娅她一个人......把那个龙女的攻击挡住了？
messages.tl: Amiya, she alone... blocked the attack of the dragon girl?
No... that power is too big...!
No problem... I have no problem...
I want to... I want to protect everyone!

messages.zh: 不可以！！那样的话，你的戒指会——！
messages.tl: No! ! In that case, your ring will be -!

messages.zh: 哪怕会带来灾难，哪怕我会......！
messages.tl: Even if it will bring disaster, even if I will...!

messages.zh: 我也不能......再看着重要的人......
messages.tl: I can't... look at important people again...

messages.zh: 把你的重担，也分给我们一些吧。
messages.tl: Give us some of your burdens too.
I wish you nowhere in the future.
